    summary: "Kidron is a refuge planet in Elrood Sector for those who have earned the enmity of the powerful, wealthy, or dangerous. Imperial intelligence assessed it as a potential nest of Rebel sympathizers but concluded the residents are simply fugitives from local law enforcers, bounty hunters, collection agents, and gangsters. The planet poses no threat to the Empire. The Orfite species is native to the sector and can be found here. Kidron is along the Elrood-Derilyn Trade Route and a minor trade route leads from Kidron to Dega through the Degan Gas Clouds.",
