    summary: "Kuras III lies beyond The Drift — a massive stellar gas cloud that has prevented exploration of the farthest reaches of Elrood Sector. The Drift makes starship sensors unreliable and forces ships to navigate at torturously slow sublight speeds, taking years to cross even the narrowest portion. No routes exist around The Drift. The Kuras system remains completely unexplored, offering a unique ecosystem, new forms of intelligent life, and adventure waiting to be discovered. Gamemasters are encouraged to make exploration a prominent campaign theme.",
