    summary: "Carosi XII is one of the few planets to openly support the New Republic. Originally a frozen ice ball, it was terraformed over decades after the sun Carosi expanded into a red giant and devoured the inner five planets including the Carosite homeworld (Carosi IV). The Carosites are gentle, furry bipeds (1.3-1.7m) with extraordinary medical talents — their first aid skill starts at 5D and they gain +2D brawling when protecting patients. They operate the Sudden Restoration, a galaxy-roaming hospital ship providing free medical care. The Carosites refuse to install cybernetic enhancements (prosthetics only). Hot springs in crystalline caves grant an extra healing roll per day after 2 hours of soaking. A hidden New Republic outpost (8 X-wings, 8 Y-wings, 208 personnel) is built into a mountainside.",
