    ofNote: "Carosites: furry bipeds, first aid 5D automatic, +2D brawling protecting patients/helpless. Reproduce only twice in lifetime (litters of 1-6). Lifespan 120 years. Verbal promises completely binding. Medical droids reprogrammed at half cost on Carosi XII. Sudden Restoration: modified Kuat Class C Frigate hospital ship (330m, 220 crew + 380 medical, 2 X-wing escorts). Hot Springs: +1 extra natural healing roll/day. Refuse cybernetic enhancements — prosthetics only. Medical metaphors pervade language. 'The Preventers' faction advocates aggressive anti-Imperial action. Rinacats: mountain predators (PER 5D, tireless trackers, can go 1 month without water). Bars heavily taxed — dietary advice given constantly by everyone."
