    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.52",
    summary: "Ragnar is the home base of the Ragnar Syndicate, one of the biggest and most professional bounty hunter syndicates in the Outer Rim Territories, slowly gaining ground on more established galaxy-wide syndicates. Located in Merel Sector.",
    locations: "Ragnar Syndicate headquarters.",
    ofNote: "Home of the Ragnar Syndicate — one of the largest bounty hunter syndicates in the Outer Rim. Has several master bounty hunters, roughly ten times as many veterans, and countless novices. Large enough to give pause to the best Special Ops groups. Operates primarily in Merel, Astal, Dail, Skine, Lol, and Portmoak sectors. Works in groups of 4-10 hunters, always including 1-2 novices for training. Also takes contracts for siege-breaking, anti-terrorist operations, sabotage, and quasi-mercenary work — can hire mercenary companies for additional firepower. Advancement strictly on merit: ~5 years to second-in-command, ~3 more to team leader. Merel Sector Moff Tregar uses the syndicate for missions that would embarrass the Imperial military."
