    summary: "Skine is home to the Skine Bounty Hunter College, a specialist syndicate dealing almost entirely with 'vagrant' fugitives — those who evade capture by constantly moving across the galaxy in their own starships.",
    locations: "Skine Bounty Hunter College headquarters.",
    ofNote: "Home of the Skine Bounty Hunter College — a specialist bounty hunter syndicate with a success rate more than twice the industry average. Specializes in cold trails and tenuous leads. For 100,000+ credits, the College will trace anyone sighted at least once in the last 15 standard years. All members typically have search, investigation, and related skills at 7D+. The College is a widespread net of hunters and informants covering much of the galaxy, particularly strong in the Outer Rim, Wild Space, and Unknown Regions. They won't give up until every last lead has been chased down. The Mandel family of Fabritech Inc. recently hired the College to find Samire Mandel, missing for 11 years. GG10 details: ~100-200 active hunters, 2,754 support staff. Run by Executive Council. Specializes in bounties over 5 standard years outstanding. 10% gap split among all participating hunters. Sponsorship by 2 active members required."
