    locations: "House Paramexor guild headquarters.",
    ofNote: "Home of the Paramexor Guild of Hunters. Guild Master: Janq Paramexor — paralyzed ex-military officer confined to a mobile life support pod for over 25 years, driven by a hatred of senseless killing. 623 hunters, 1,740 support staff. Only accepts bounties involving murder or attempted murder. Paradoxically, no acquisition hunted by a Paramexor member has ever been taken alive. Membership deliberately kept under 1,000; hunters receive every possible service and personal luxury. Said that any member would willingly die for their guild master. Moderate but increasing influence. Operations in Galactic Core and surrounding regions. Sponsorship by 3 members required. Dues: 300 cr/year, 3% gap."
