    ofNote: "Home of House Renliss Bounty Hunters Guild. Co-founders: Jalindas and Gratina Renliss (former Imperial Intelligence deep-cover agents who went rogue after being abandoned by their male team members). 244 active huntresses, 1,249 support staff. Only accepts female hunters ('huntresses') and only bounties on males. 7 years in operation with marginal but increasing influence. Evidence suggests one or both founders were Imperial Intelligence — the guild still receives considerable Intelligence business. Rumored that more than one wealthy Imperial statesman has met an untimely end at the hands of a Renliss huntress fulfilling a personal bounty paid by the late statesman's widow. Operations in Galactic Core, Core Worlds, Colonies, Inner Rim, Hutt Space, Corporate Sector, and selected Outer Rim sectors. Personal selection by CEOs required. Personal dues arrangement, 5% gap."
