    ofNote: "The nature of the terrain convinced the Rebel Alliance to install the comm center here — even if the Empire located it, an extended ground campaign would be required to take it. The comm center is now firmly under Imperial control. The loss of this unique broadcast center, with its hiridiu crystal signal boost, will be difficult for the New Republic to recover from."
