    summary: "The closest Myrkr gets to a true population center, Hyllyard City is a little piece of civilization on the edge of a great forest. Like Mos Eisley on Tatooine and other frontier towns, it consists of a few starship landing pits and a close-packed collection of makeshift structures. The small houses and commercial buildings are crammed tightly together, built in a familiar wheel pattern around a large open square. Narrow streets run between the buildings, and a few wide avenues radiate like spokes from the center of town.",
