    summary: "Sarka is a planet of steaming jungles and vast tracts of marshland, home to a dazzling variety of insects, plants, and animals, including the Sarkans — the planet's only sapient species. The majority of Sarkans live in an elaborate system of interlocking caves and subterranean passageways, usually located adjacent to underground hot springs which compensate for cool Sarkan nights. Despite their crude outward appearance, the caves are very modern, incorporating shops, restaurants, holo-theatres, and other amenities.",
