    ofNote: "Among the major exports are Sarkan Nova Rubies, mined from the cave networks. These crystals are common on Sarka and used for illumination in darker cave reaches, but are highly prized off-world for their brilliant luminescence — the Sarkans are amused that these common stones can be so valued. Sarka has parlayed its gem wealth into political clout, and Sarkan ambassadors are now among the powerful factions in the New Republic. Sarka is currently negotiating a shipping treaty and hoping to lure a New Republic military detachment to cut down on smuggling, piracy, and Imperial incursions."
