    locations: "",
    ofNote: "Svivren is completely neutral in the civil war. Svivreni law forbids the presence of any personal weapon, and well-armed security troops enforce that law efficiently. Any violent actions on Svivren result in immediate and public execution — as such, Svivren has a low crime rate. Even smugglers tend to avoid the planet: if the Mon Calamari made smuggling difficult, the Svivreni made it dangerous."
