    summary: "Iziz is the great walled city of Onderon, covering more than a thousand square miles and housing several million inhabitants. It grew from a practical necessity — defense against the warbeasts that periodically crossed from the moon Dxun via an atmosphere bridge during summer months. The city's massive walls have defined Onderonian civilization for centuries, separating the protected citizen population inside from the exiled beast-riders in the wilderness beyond. With the end of the Beast Wars and the rise of Queen Galia and Odon Kira, Iziz is entering a new era — the dark side influence that pervaded the royal palace for generations has been cleansed, and Onderon is now seeking Republic membership.",
