    ofNote: "GOVERNMENT: The lingering remains of Esselian power lie primarily in the hands of President Cambira Ralle, an aging Clone Wars veteran who never opposes Palpatine's edicts and is essentially powerless. Moff Graffe's official residence is here. Imperial Governor Griff Takel is a moderate and capable administrator, balancing Imperial demands with Esselian sensibilities. Both Graffe and Takel work to ensure Esselian loyalty via pro-Imperial marches, rallies, and 'spontaneous' pro-Palpatine demonstrations. | INDUSTRY: Although no major manufacturers are headquartered on Esseles, most Bormea sector corporations have production facilities here to take advantage of the concentration of engineers and favorable tax base. Aether Hypernautics, Sienar Fleet Systems, Les Tech, and Gowix Computers all have important factories here. | MILITARY: Sector capital with deep Imperial investment. Esseles naval bases directly command the two Darpa sector border outposts (2LC/Blue and 1B6/Green) near the Ringali Nebula. The 2LC/Blue outpost is staffed by 2LC/Blue TIE Pilot crews. Veshiv's Veteran Stormtrooper squads are also deployed in the Esseles system."
