    summary: "Homeworld of Captain Iolan Gendarr, former Imperial Navy officer who served under Captain Needa aboard the Star Destroyer Avenger before being promoted to command the Star Destroyer Reliance.",
    locations: "",
    ofNote: "WANTED — IOLAN GENDARR: New Republic bounty of 75,000 credits. Wanted alive. Charges: treason, sedition, murder of New Republic personnel, destruction of New Republic property. Gendarr fled Jardeen IV after the Battle of Endor, aiding General Arndall Lott's escape before Republic forces arrived. The Reliance has since led several attacks in New Republic territory, utilizing Scimitar assault bomber bombardments and AT-AT/AT-ST ground assaults. | CRACKEN'S PERSONAL NOTES: There can be little doubt that Gendarr and Lott now serve the Empire together. The correspondence of sightings of the Reliance and the attacks by Lott's walker divisions cannot be pure coincidence."
