    summary: "Laerron Woern's pirate base, located within one of the largest asteroids in the Drup Asteroid Field in the remote Drup's Star system. The mineral composition of the asteroids renders standard sensor readings useless — the entire field reads as a dense area filled with minerals, making it impossible to detect other ships except in close proximity.",
