    summary: "Korad is an insignificant stop on the Elrood-Derilyn Trade Route. A ring of ship wrecks and parts circles the planet. The north pole has a small landing pad; most of the rest of the dry, dusty planet is covered by unimaginably vast salvage yards. Machinery, ships, vehicles, and scrap metal are piled high in huge mounds. The planet's atmosphere and water are poisoned by leaking reactors and other contaminants, requiring the use of breath masks on the surface. The planet is the perfect place to dump unwanted material or find rare starship components. It's rumored that this planet is also the site of more shadowy activities.",
