    majorImports: "High technology, agricultural products, medical supplies",
    source: "WEG40137 Instant Adventures",
    summary: "Obas is a superheated volcanic wasteland in the Expansion Region. The extreme temperatures require vacuum suits for survival — each round without protection risks 3D damage from heat and radiation. The Rebel Alliance maintains a hidden base here, taking advantage of the planet's inhospitable environment to discourage Imperial interest. The base requires coolant hydro-valves to prevent its systems from melting into slag.",
    locations: "",
    ofNote: "REBEL BASE: A hidden Alliance outpost built into a cliff face with massive doors to keep out extreme temperatures. Houses 62 personnel along with weaponry, data, and medical supplies. The base's cooling systems require regular maintenance and replacement hydro-valves. | ENVIRONMENTAL HAZARD: Searing temperatures cause 3D damage per round to unprotected characters. Vacuum suits provide immunity. Most systems — lighting, communications, hatchway controls — fail when exposed to the intense heat."
