    summary: "Butler's Cove was originally discovered by a pirate named Butler who intended to use it as a base for raids into the Demophon system. Unfortunately, Butler was killed on the first such raid and his pirate band scattered. The planet has been uninhabited since then. It was chosen by Dr. Soron Hegerty as the new homeworld for evacuated Ssither from the doomed planet Jatee, as its heavy gravity, temperate climate, and lack of Human presence make it suitable for the telepathic reptilian species.",
