    summary: "Also called the Sisar Terminal, Nwarcol Point is the 'small giant' of the Sisar refueling posts. A relic of ancient Hutt expansion, it has benefited from an advantageous position at the Salin Corridor intersection and direct investment from Xizor Transport Systems. Most small and medium transports heading Coreward from Hutt Space find Nwarcol Point an ideal refueling station before continuing through the Outer Rim Territories.",
